**Problem**: CRLF line endings cause Docker script failures
**Files affected**: `*.sh`, `*.sql` in `configs/postgres/`, `db/migrations/`

**Solution**:
```powershell
# Fix line endings before Docker operations
Get-Content configs/postgres/postgresql_setup.sh | Set-Content -Encoding UTF8 -Path configs/postgres/postgresql_setup.sh
Get-Content db/migrations/init_db.sh | Set-Content -Encoding UTF8 -Path db/migrations/init_db.sh

# Git auto-fix
git config --global core.autocrlf input
